				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm guessing it's for the odd occassion when you are fighting multiple mobs and one of them AEs, and the pet will change targets. 
<br />

<br />
Another use I can see for it would be pet offtanking. Necros don't use this a lot, but it's something that happens often on my beastlord. If you wanted your pet to offtank one mob for a short time, and then turn and assist the mob you yourself are killing, it's nearly impossible without this command. The pet will turn and attack the OT mob since it's the highest on its aggro list from beating it senseless.
<br />

<br />
Overall though, not something I planned to rush into getting. It's the next AA on my list since i'm done with just about every other OOW one.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
