				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ok, not worthless when used correctly.
<br />

<br />
Cyborg had it pegged; I removed it from my Attack hotkey and made a seperate one, just /pet focus. This I click when pet first summoned just like turning off Taunt, and it sticks on all further attacks by pet, keeping it locked on the target.
<br />

<br />
It does, as mentioned by Pype, fade somehow either after zoning or un-Suspending. However, once I /focus in a particular zone, it stays so.
<br />

<br />
Graal Macabre, Quellious</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
